700120f-a.text:
E. 146th Street, adjoining the southwest corner of Third Avenue, showing the Mott Haven Reformed Dutch Church and parish house. The parish house, a two-story brick house, was formerly the Bronson Catholic Club.

P.L. Sperr
April 28, 1941
